'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 19''' was the 19th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]'', published for [[March]]/[[April]] [[1999]]. It reprinted material from [[Star Wars Insider 42|''Star Wars Insider'' 42]].

==Contents==
===Departments===
*[[Feel the Force]]
*[[Jawa's Corner|Jawas' Corner]]
*[[Prequel Update]]
*[[In the Star Wars Universe|In the ''Star Wars'' Universe]] &mdash; [[Tim Rose]] {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 42}}
*[[Prequel Profile]] &mdash; [[Nick Dudman]] {{C|''Star Wars Insider'' 42}}
*Book Round-Up {{C|by [[Andy Lane]]}}
*[[Comlink (department)|Comlink]]

===Features===
*"[[George Lucas Down Under]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 42|''Star Wars Insider'' 42]]}}
*"[[Frank Oz: Blizzard of Oz]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 42}}
*"[[Darth Maul: Evil Has a New Name]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 42}}
*"The Best of ''Star Wars''"
*"[[Star Wars Short-Cuts|''Star Wars'' Short-Cuts]]"
*:<small>The second part of our comprehensive guide to video game cheats past and present.</small>
*"[[THX: The Sound And The Fury]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 42}}

